revision.text: Possibly: The voyage of La Pérouse round the world in the years 1785, 1786, 1787, and 1788, with the nautical tables / arranged by M.L.A. Milet Mureau, Inspector of Fortifications and member of several literary societies at Paris ; to which is prefixed, Narrative of an interesting voyage from Manilla to St. Blaise ; and annexed, Travels over the continent, with the dispatches of La Pérouse in 1787 and 1788, by M. de Lesseps ; translated from the French ; illustrated with fifty-one plates ; in two volumes. (London : Printed for John Stockdale, Piccadilly, 1798). http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b1933887~S1
